<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>Thank you for previously holding business insurance with Kingsbridge.<br><br>It’s not too late to take out a new insurance policy with us - it’s important to note that if you don't have another insurance policy in place,&nbsp;<b>your business may not be covered against claims</b>.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>It would only take 5-10 minutes to provide you with a comprehensive quote -</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm3g-k74-js2/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>book a call with me</b></a><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, you can reply to let me know a good time to call or contact me on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">07974533903</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
